{
"#name"
:
{
"rule"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"Rules to rule · 用规则统领代码与智能体输出质量"
,
"en"
:
"Rules to rule · use rules to govern code and AI agent output quality"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x rule [-r ruleset] [--yml|--json|--tsv|--csv]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule lint [--json|--tsv] <file|dir>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule scan [-r ruleset] [-o file] [file ... | :preset]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule check [-r ruleset] [file ... | :preset]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule audit [-r ruleset] [-o dir] [file ... | :preset]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule fix [-r ruleset] [-n rounds] [--report file] [file ... | :preset]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule refine [-r ruleset] <report_dir>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule evolve [-r ruleset] <target_dir>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule preset [ls|which]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x rule which"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"通过 YAML 规则集对代码进行质量检查。提供三级精度：scan（贪心快筛）、check（全局合规检查）、audit（逐条评分审计）。\n另有 lint（jq 静态验证 rule.yml 格式）、fix（自主修复循环）、refine（精调规则）、evolve（适应项目）。\n规则以 YAML 文件按类别组织，每条规则包含 id、name、desc、level、tldr 等字段。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Check code quality against YAML rulesets. Three precision levels: scan (greedy coarse scan), check (full compliance check), audit (per-rule scoring).\nPlus lint (jq static validation of rule.yml), fix (autonomous fix loop), refine (improve rule precision), evolve (adapt rules to project).\nRules are organized in YAML files by category, each containing id, name, desc, level, tldr fields.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"三级检查精度不同，场景不同。scan（~1 分钟）快筛找最严重问题，适合 agent 内循环快速迭代；check（~1-10 分钟）全局对照所有规则，确认无遗漏后再进入 audit；audit（~10-60 分钟）逐条精确评分出报告，适合最终验证。先 scan 迭代，再 check 前哨确认，最后 audit 出报告。"
,
"en"
:
"Three precision levels for different scenarios. scan (~1 min) coarse scan for top issues, ideal for agent inner-loop; check (~1-10 min) full coverage of all rules, confirms nothing is missed before audit; audit (~10-60 min) per-rule scoring, for final validation. Workflow: scan iteratively → check as scout → audit for final report."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"scan 采用贪心策略：每轮只找 1-5 个最严重的问题。懂规则的 agent 会在修复时顺便处理其他潜在违规，减少迭代轮次。"
,
"en"
:
"scan uses a greedy strategy: find 1-5 most critical issues per round. A rule-aware agent proactively fixes other potential violations while at it, reducing iteration rounds."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"fix 是自主修复循环：内部反复执行 check → 修复 → recheck，直到全部合规或达到轮次上限。"
,
"en"
:
"fix is an autonomous loop: internally runs check → fix → recheck until all rules pass or max rounds reached."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"refine 根据审计报告精调规则（纵向：同一条规则越调越准）；evolve 根据项目代码适配规则（横向：规则集越长越全）。"
,
"en"
:
"refine improves rule precision from audit reports (vertical: same rule gets sharper); evolve adapts ruleset to project (horizontal: ruleset grows to cover more)."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"x check <file> 等同于 x rule check <file>，x audit <file> 等同于 x rule audit <file>。人类可使用短命令。"
,
"en"
:
"x check <file> equals x rule check <file>; x audit <file> equals x rule audit <file>. Humans can use short commands."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"规则集默认从工作区 .x-cmd/rule 目录加载，也可通过 -r 指定任意目录。"
,
"en"
:
"Rulesets are loaded from .x-cmd/rule in the workspace by default, or via -r flag."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"规则 YAML 格式：id → name → apply → level(error/warn/info) → desc → tldr(wrong/right)。"
,
"en"
:
"Rule YAML format: id → name → apply → level(error/warn/info) → desc → tldr(wrong/right)."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"使用 :preset 引用预定义规则集（如 x audit :os 检查系统状态，x audit :ssh 检查 SSH 配置）。用 x rule preset ls 查看所有可用 preset。"
,
"en"
:
"Use :preset to reference predefined rulesets (e.g. x audit :os for OS checks, x audit :ssh for SSH config). Run x rule preset ls to see all available presets."
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule"
,
"cn"
:
"列出当前工作区的所有规则（默认子命令为 ls）"
,
"en"
:
"List all rules in current workspace (default subcmd is ls)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule scan adv/index.yml"
,
"cn"
:
"快筛 adv/index.yml，只找 1-5 个最严重的问题"
,
"en"
:
"Coarse scan adv/index.yml, find 1-5 most critical issues only"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule check -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集目录，全局合规检查 src/"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset directory, full compliance check src/"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule fix -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"自主修复循环，反复检查并修复直到合规"
,
"en"
:
"Autonomous fix loop, check and fix iteratively until compliant"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule audit -r /path/to/ruleset lib/"
,
"cn"
:
"审计检查整个 lib/ 目录，生成逐条评分报告"
,
"en"
:
"Audit check entire lib/ directory with per-rule scoring report"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule refine /path/to/report"
,
"cn"
:
"根据审计报告精调规则"
,
"en"
:
"Refine rules based on audit report"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule evolve src/"
,
"cn"
:
"根据项目代码适配规则集"
,
"en"
:
"Adapt ruleset to project code patterns"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule scan :os"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 :os preset 快筛系统状态"
,
"en"
:
"Coarse scan system status using :os preset"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule preset ls"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有可用的预设规则集"
,
"en"
:
"List all available preset rulesets"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Check"
:
[
"lint"
,
"scan"
,
"check"
,
"audit"
]
,
"#subcmd:Fix"
:
[
"fix"
]
,
"#subcmd:Evolve"
:
[
"refine"
,
"evolve"
]
,
"#subcmd:Reference"
:
[
"ls"
,
"which"
,
"preset"
]
,
"#subcmd:Preset"
:
[
"preset"
]
,
"scan"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"快筛，每轮只找 1-5 个最严重的违规项，适合迭代修复"
,
"en"
:
"Coarse scan, find 1-5 most critical violations per round, ideal for iterative fixing"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule scan -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集，快筛 src/"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset, coarse scan src/"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule scan -o result.tsv src/"
,
"cn"
:
"快筛并将结果写入 result.tsv"
,
"en"
:
"Coarse scan and write results to result.tsv"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"-o"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出文件路径（默认输出到标准输出）"
,
"en"
:
"Output file path (default: stdout)"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要检查的文件或目录"
,
"en"
:
"Files or directories to check"
}
}
}
,
"lint"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"用 jq 对 rule.yml 做纯静态结构验证（无需 LLM）。检查 YAML 语法、规则 ID 格式、必填字段、level 枚举、字段类型等。适合在提交前做快速自检。"
,
"en"
:
"Pure static structural validation of rule.yml using jq (no LLM). Checks YAML syntax, rule ID format, required fields, level enum, field types. Ideal for pre-commit self-check."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule lint lib/po6/local.yml"
,
"cn"
:
"验证单条规则文件"
,
"en"
:
"Validate a single rule file"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule lint lib/po6/"
,
"cn"
:
"验证目录下所有规则文件"
,
"en"
:
"Validate all rule files in a directory"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule lint --json lib/meta.rule.yml"
,
"cn"
:
"JSON 格式输出结构化结果"
,
"en"
:
"Output structured results in JSON"
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"零错误（error）才能通过；warn 和 info 仅作提示。"
,
"en"
:
"Zero errors required to pass; warn and info are advisory only."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"YAML 解析失败会在 TSV 中报告为 meta-rule-010 错误。"
,
"en"
:
"YAML parse failure is reported as meta-rule-010 error in TSV."
}
]
}
,
"check"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"全局合规检查，对照所有规则输出违规项，以 TSV 格式输出到标准输出（仅 score < 81 的条目）。常作为 audit 的前哨确认。"
,
"en"
:
"Full compliance check against all rules, output violations as TSV to stdout (score < 81 only). Often used as scout before audit."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule check -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集，全局合规检查 src/"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset, full compliance check src/"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要检查的文件或目录"
,
"en"
:
"Files or directories to check"
}
}
}
,
"audit"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"审计级检查，分两阶段执行：先生成规则-文件对应表，再逐条评分（0-100）。输出详细 TSV 报告文件（每条规则一个文件）。"
,
"en"
:
"Audit check in two phases: first generate rule-file mapping, then per-rule scoring (0-100). Outputs detailed TSV report files (one per rule)."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"评分标准：100=完全合规，81-99=小问题可接受，51-80=需改进，0-50=严重违规。"
,
"en"
:
"Scoring: 100=full compliance, 81-99=minor acceptable, 51-80=needs improvement, 0-50=significant violation."
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule audit -r /path/to/ruleset lib/"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集目录，审计检查整个 lib/ 目录"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset directory, audit check entire lib/ directory"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule audit -o /tmp/report lib/main"
,
"cn"
:
"审计检查并指定报告输出目录"
,
"en"
:
"Audit check with custom report output directory"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"-o"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"报告输出目录（默认数据目录下 rule/report）"
,
"en"
:
"Report output directory (default: rule/report under data dir)"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要检查的文件或目录"
,
"en"
:
"Files or directories to check"
}
}
}
,
"fix"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自主修复循环，内部反复执行 check → 修复 → recheck，直到全部合规或达到轮次上限（默认 5 轮）。"
,
"en"
:
"Autonomous fix loop, internally runs check → fix → recheck until all rules pass or max rounds (default 5) reached."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"fix 过程中，懂规则的 agent 会顺便修复非报告中的潜在违规。"
,
"en"
:
"During fix, a rule-aware agent proactively fixes other potential violations not in the report."
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule fix -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"自主修复 src/ 直到合规"
,
"en"
:
"Autonomously fix src/ until compliant"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule fix -n 10 src/"
,
"cn"
:
"最多修复 10 轮"
,
"en"
:
"Fix up to 10 rounds"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule fix --report /tmp/issue.tsv src/"
,
"cn"
:
"根据已有报告直接修复，跳过首轮扫描"
,
"en"
:
"Fix from an existing report, skip initial scan"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"-n"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"最大修复轮次（默认 5）"
,
"en"
:
"Max fix rounds (default 5)"
}
}
,
"--report"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"已有的违规报告文件，跳过首轮扫描直接修复（默认：无，首轮自动扫描）"
,
"en"
:
"Existing violation report file, skip initial scan (default: none, auto-scan on first round)"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要修复的文件或目录"
,
"en"
:
"Files or directories to fix"
}
}
}
,
"refine"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"根据审计报告精调规则。分析误报和漏检，改写规则的 desc、tldr、apply 等字段使其更精确。"
,
"en"
:
"Refine rules based on audit report. Analyze false positives and missed violations, rewrite rule desc, tldr, apply fields for precision."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule refine /path/to/report"
,
"cn"
:
"根据审计报告精调规则"
,
"en"
:
"Refine rules based on audit report"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule refine -r /path/to/ruleset /path/to/report"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集，根据报告精调"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset, refine based on report"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"审计报告目录（x rule audit 的输出）"
,
"en"
:
"Audit report directory (output from x rule audit)"
}
}
}
,
"evolve"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"根据项目代码适配规则集。分析代码模式和约定，创建新规则或调整现有规则以适应项目。"
,
"en"
:
"Adapt ruleset to project. Analyze code patterns and conventions, create new rules or adjust existing ones to fit the project."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule evolve src/"
,
"cn"
:
"根据 src/ 代码适配规则集"
,
"en"
:
"Adapt ruleset based on src/ code"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule evolve -r /path/to/ruleset src/"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集，根据代码适配"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset, adapt based on code"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要分析的项目目录"
,
"en"
:
"Project directory to analyze"
}
}
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出规则集中所有可用规则"
,
"en"
:
"List all available rules in the ruleset"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule ls --tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"TSV 格式列出所有规则，适合管道处理"
,
"en"
:
"List all rules in TSV format, suitable for piping"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule ls -r /path/to/ruleset"
,
"cn"
:
"指定规则集目录，列出其中所有规则"
,
"en"
:
"Specify ruleset directory, list all rules in it"
}
]
,
"-r"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"规则集目录路径"
,
"en"
:
"Ruleset directory path"
}
}
,
"--yml"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"YAML 格式输出（默认）"
,
"en"
:
"Output in YAML format (default)"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
}
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"CSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in CSV format"
}
}
}
,
"which"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示当前工作区的规则集目录路径（.x-cmd/rule）"
,
"en"
:
"Show the ruleset directory path for the current workspace (.x-cmd/rule)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x rule which"
,
"cn"
:
"查看默认规则集路径"
,
"en"
:
"Show default ruleset path"
}
]
}
,
"preset"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"管理预定义规则集（preset）。Preset 以 :name 形式在 scan/check/audit/fix 中引用，如 x audit :os。"
,
"en"
:
"Manage predefined rulesets (presets). Referenced as :name in scan/check/audit/fix, e.g. x audit :os."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
